NZ Performance Car - December 2013

112 Pages | True PDF | English | 23 MB 


NZ Performance Car is the country's performance import authority, no questions asked! Each month the very best of NZ's modified import car scene is served up, with everything from high horsepower haulers and gleaming show stoppers to action-packed events coming your way. NZ Performance Car delivers all you could ever ask for from the modified car scene. It's New Zealand's largest selling monthly motoring magazine, and for good reason:it leaves the others for dust!
